description.value: GooN is a digital currency, which is an alternative form of payment created using meticulous encryption algorithms. It functions both as a currency and a virtual accounting system. We hope that you will not only join us for the journey but stay for the after party. We will develop more and more uses for GooN as we grow. Our roadmap, whitepaper and info will be available.. We are here to answer questions and glad to be a member of the Cardano Ecosystem. Thank you for taking the time to read this.
